divs: Sighting DetailsOn October 23rd while returning from Hico Texas Stephenville Texas on highway 6 I observed three bright orange objects traveling at an high rate of speed to the west. They were only visible for three or four minutes then went out of sight. They did travel one right behind the other but were not consistant with any conventional aircraft that I am aware of or have seen in this area.
